---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-surface p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-accent">About Me</h1>
    <img src="/your-profile-image.jpg" alt="Your Name" class="w-64 h-64 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 object-cover" />
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      Hello! I'm [Your Name], a passionate web developer and data scientist with a keen interest in machine learning and artificial intelligence.
    </p>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      This blog is a showcase of my journey through the intersecting worlds of web development, data science, and machine learning. Here, I share my thoughts, experiences, and insights on these fascinating fields.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">About This Project</h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      This blog itself is a testament to my passion for modern web technologies. Built with Astro, it leverages the power of static site generation while allowing for dynamic content. The project utilizes a robust tech stack:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-text-secondary">
      <li>Astro for blazing-fast static site generation</li>
      <li>GitHub Actions for continuous integration and deployment</li>
      <li>Google Cloud Platform (GCP) for hosting and infrastructure</li>
      <li>Google Kubernetes Engine (GKE) for containerized deployment</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      This combination of technologies allows me to focus on creating content while ensuring high performance, scalability, and ease of maintenance.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">The Intersection of Web, Data, and AI</h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      My work often sits at the crossroads of web development, data science, and machine learning. I'm fascinated by how these fields complement each other:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-text-secondary">
      <li>Web development provides the interface for data-driven applications</li>
      <li>Data science uncovers insights that inform both web experiences and ML models</li>
      <li>Machine learning algorithms power intelligent features in web applications</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
      Through this blog, I aim to explore these interconnections, sharing projects, tutorials, and insights that span these exciting domains.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">Connect With Me</h2>
    <div class="flex space-x-4">
      <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" class="text-link hover:text-accent">Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" class="text-link hover:text-accent">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" class="text-link hover:text-accent">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>